{"tid":540680,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"唉，今次都唔知點算好","createTime":"2018-01-25T16:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T17:20:47.000Z","uid":144264,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"82d929884fc9a24e6a09e380c08b4956dcb93cea","tid":540680,"uid":144264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T16:53:26.000Z","msg":"岩岩先翻到屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近公司好多野煩，心情超差，放工未食野咁就入左間粥店求其食啲野算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫左碗粥，老細清油器櫃見仲有條油炸鬼就問我要唔要埋佢，我心諗都好耐無食過就要埋佢啦，咁就行左出去拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知我拎完條油炸鬼翻埋位既時候，有個大概五歲既細佬係咁落胡椒粉落我碗粥到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成樽都落曬咁濟，我就勁嬲咁同佢老母理論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知佢老母答我：「細佬仔喺咁伯厭架啦，使死咩一碗粥」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當時完全失去理智，加上近排壓力，我直接拎住手上條油炸鬼往係咁車落去佢個仔個頭到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大概打咗五六下，比老闆攔住先停落黎，個細路無咩傷，不過喊到豬頭咁，搞到警察過左嚟，帶咗翻去做筆錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢老豆話咩真係估都估唔到有人拎油炸鬼打自己個仔叫我道歉，我堅決唔道歉，要告就告啦。最後我想問下佢可以告我咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:條油炸鬼過曬氣淋到成條廢老賓州咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36141290e99067ce93e7dd8a18b3032c1527a406","tid":540680,"uid":19932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:03:06.000Z","msg":"先道歉 無謂惹屎上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nEQ低到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425705006e01ca39358de1f333ce1497d01f7b8d","tid":540680,"uid":71826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:05:18.000Z","msg":"你又係衰郁手在先<br />\n叫老細換過碗 話呢碗唔會埋單咪算<br />\n推比個老母食"},{"pid":"1647579d69d46774cbe02ac313f70be2f86e038d","tid":540680,"uid":4578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:08:20.000Z","msg":"屌 成碗粥車落個西女人到啦<br />\n唔撚識教仔？"},{"pid":"fdd5846bf9243cc5f4e96592e3815cba90b68c99","tid":540680,"uid":137275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:09:56.000Z","msg":"Psp法式面包改編"},{"pid":"bb7e21c446b48b849615966f427e933725c25e97","tid":540680,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9bd8846f80a503c7d3913c5474962cd37153aad","tid":540680,"uid":86776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:15:21.000Z","msg":"仆...你老母500蚊碗雲吞..."},{"pid":"6476e8abf1d7f3fbebbee221dc912221aedf07d1","tid":540680,"uid":75368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:16:52.000Z","msg":"不要玩食物"},{"pid":"e3aec0e607c30d47c0477a53596014c482c7aaad","tid":540680,"uid":144264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6476e8abf1d7f3fbebbee221dc912221aedf07d1","tid":540680,"uid":75368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:16:52.000Z","msg":"不要玩食物"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:18:25.000Z","msg":"最後有食埋條油炸鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會話我毁壞證物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35705c7da00c9c2ea648ebdee206af20533d39b0","tid":540680,"uid":144264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1647579d69d46774cbe02ac313f70be2f86e038d","tid":540680,"uid":4578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:08:20.000Z","msg":"屌 成碗粥車落個西女人到啦<br />\n唔撚識教仔？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T17:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經當條油炸鬼喺武器喺咁車喺咁車<img src=